section.partition
  .partition__wrapper
    .partition__header
      h2(tabindex="0").partition__title ЛОФТ ПЕРЕГОРОДКИ
      ul.partition__advantages-list
        li.partition__advantages-item(data-aos="zoom-in-right" data-aos-delay="150" data-aos-duration="1000") <span>01</span> Решают проблему зонирования офиса
        li.partition__advantages-item(data-aos="zoom-in-right" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-duration="1000") <span>02</span> Разделении рабочих, гостевых и других зон
        li.partition__advantages-item(data-aos="zoom-in-right" data-aos-delay="250" data-aos-duration="1000") <span>03</span> Эффект зрительного расширения пространства

    ul.partition__list
      li.partition__item
        picture
          source(type="image/webp" srcset="img/lqip/static/partition_home@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_home@1x.webp 1x, img/static/partition_home@2x.webp 2x")
          img.partition__img.lazyload.blur-up(src="img/lqip/static/partition_home@1x.jpg" data-src="img/static/partition_home@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_home@2x.jpg 2x" alt="Перегородки для дома")

        p.partition__item-description Для дома

      li.partition__item
        picture
          source(type="image/webp" srcset="img/lqip/static/partition_office@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_office@1x.webp 1x, img/static/partition_office@2x.webp 2x")
          img.partition__img.lazyload.blur-up(src="img/lqip/static/partition_office@1x.jpg" data-src="img/static/partition_office@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_office@2x.jpg 2x" alt="Перегородки для офиса")

        p.partition__item-description В офис

      li.partition__item
        picture
          source(type="image/webp" srcset="img/lqip/static/partition_rest@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_rest@1x.webp 1x, img/static/partition_rest@2x.webp 2x")
          img.partition__img.lazyload.blur-up(src="img/lqip/static/partition_rest@1x.jpg" data-src="img/static/partition_rest@1x.jpg" data-srcset="img/static/partition_rest@2x.jpg 2x" alt="Перегородки для ресторанов и кафе")

        p.partition__item-description Для кафе и ресторанов

    a(href="#").partition__link.m-link ПОДРОБНЕЕ
      svg(width="50" height="6")
        use(xlink:href="#icon-arr")
